\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
after "eq. (11.19)"
key "dresselhaus_group_2008"
literal "true"

\end_inset

, eq.
 (11.19) and the character table for 
\begin_inset Formula $D_{3h}$
\end_inset

