\begin_inset Formula $\hat{P}_{ab}^{\left(\Gamma\right)}$
\end_inset

 defined by 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
after "eq. (4.28)"
key "dresselhaus_group_2008"
literal "true"

